# rz_negpi8 — Rz(-π/8) = e^{i(π/16)Z}. 반각 Pauli-Z 회전(2차 Suzuki step의 반각 ZZ에 필요). analytic golden.
```python id=bloq
import numpy as np
from qualtran.bloqs.basic_gates import Rz
bloq = Rz(-np.pi/8)
```
```python id=golden
import numpy as np
golden = np.diag([np.exp(1j*np.pi/16), np.exp(-1j*np.pi/16)]).astype(complex)
```
